test_data = {'email': self.user, 'password': self.password, 'api': self.api}
admin_headers = self.get_admin_headers()
response = self.app.post('/user', headers=admin_headers, data=json.dumps(
    test_data), content_type='application/json')
self.assertEqual(response.status_code, 409)
response_json = json.loads(response.data or '{}')
self.assertDictContainsSubset({'message': u'User already exists'},
    response_json)
